OL,4,CMacron asks Rwanda to forgive France
OL,5,Cover 1994 genocide role
OL,6, French President Emmanuel Macron has
OL,7, asked Rwandans to forgive France for
OL,8, its role in the 1994 Rwandan genocide
OL,9, in which about 800,000 ethnic Tutsis
OL,10, and moderate Hutus died.
OL,12,FSpeaking at the genocide memorial in
OL,13,FRwanda's capital Kigali, he said France
OL,14,Fhad not heeded warnings of impending
OL,15,Fcarnage and had for too long "valued
OL,16,Fsilence over examination of the truth".
OL,18,FBut France had not been an accomplice
OL,19,Fin the killings, Mr Macron added.
OL,21,FRwanda's leader praised his speech.
